reviewText:
Um, what can I say. The price and shipping, couldn't have asked for any better. Thank you.
The video it self, didn't learn any more then what I/We already knew. Interesting to watch.
Came with a music disk as well, haven't heard it yet. I have the book and this DVD is a very condensed version.
Didn't know what to expect yet not bad watching it either. Does make for some fun though.
